rategic partnerships and make critical business decisions aimed at creating long-term value for clients and the agency itself.  </span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"client_tabs_structure_right\" offset=\"vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"departmens_structure_col\"]</p>\r\n<h5>Head of dept</h5>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class=\"departmens_structure_col\"]</p>\r\n<h5>2 Senior SEO specialists</h5>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class=\"departmens_structure_col\"]</p>\r\n<h5>5 Junior SEO specialists</h5>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class=\"departmens_structure_col\"]</p>\r\n<h5>1 Assistant</h5>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section css=\".vc_custom_1622634434818{background-color: #f1f3f5 !important;}\" el_class=\"about_our_agency_section\"][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Rampiq\'s core values</h2>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our clients truly are our heroes. We know success is earned, not given, and running a successful business takes hard work. Our commitment to your project is matched only by our respect for your courage, stamina, and persistence. </span></p>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"624\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h4>Availability</h4>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We know the field of internet marketing can feel daunting to many business owners. That is why we have made it our goal to be readily available for your questions, concerns, and feedback. We will always keep you apprised of your campaign progress and make sure you have ownership over your marketing successes.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"623\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h4>Openness</h4>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">At Rampiq, we believe that every team member plays an important role in contributing to a project’s success. We know the field of digital marketing is constantly changing; that’s why we are always open to new ideas and new ways of thinking. We strive to keep learning, innovating, and sharing our knowledge as a team.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"625\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h4>Transparency</h4>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">At its core, marketing is about visibility and communication. We have seen first-hand the power digital marketing has to completely change the trajectory of business for the better. We believe in building strong relationships with our clients, listening to them, and fostering a culture of open, honest, and transparent communication.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section el_class=\"about_what_makes_sections\"][vc_row][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h5><b>Powerful Partnerships</b></h5>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A <a href=\"https://rampiqstg.wpengine.com/who-we-help/in-house/\">digital marketing team</a> is only as strong as the relationships they have with their clients. We view our interactions and work with clients as true partnerships, rooted in a shared vision for the business, a love of leveraging data in a thoughtful and authentic way, and a commitment to creating amazing customer experiences.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h5><b>Winning Workflows</b></h5>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Every step of your online campaigns is documented in detail by our digital marketing team using tried and true workflows. These critical organizational tools don’t just keep stakeholders on track–they help create repeatable processes your company can use for years to come, making you and your team more knowledgeable and your business more sustainable as it grows.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h5><b>Delighting in Details</b></h5>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tracking campaign performance and progress is impossible without keen attention to detail and a fervent love of numbers. The Rampiq team works closely with our clients to understand and define key performance indicators and then optimize campaigns again and again to stay accountable to them. We delight in all the small digital marketing details to bring your big picture into focus and move your company forward.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h5><b>Inspiring Innovation</b></h5>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Marketing online in the 2020s can change in the blink of an eye. As new platforms explode and more advanced digital marketing tools become available, it’s critical that businesses stay nimble and think outside of the box. Rampiq supports all our clients in finding the perfect ecosystem of <a href=\"https://rampiqstg.wpengine.com/services/\">digital marketing solutions</a> to innovate smart marketing moves and power their greatest growth yet.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h2>What makes us different</h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our passion for digital marketing paired with our</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"643\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">#Rampiq_team</h2>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_ro