.com/?post_type=logos&#038;p=174',0,'logos','',0),(185,1,'2021-05-07 06:14:28','2021-05-07 06:14:28','<p>[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How can eCommerce businesses get a competitive advantage and increase sales? What you sell, pricing and your customer service make a massive difference; but when it comes to getting more customers, that all boils down to your digital toolkit, marketing plan, and how you implement this. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here is our step-by-step strategy, showing how eCommerce brands can use this powerful list of data-driven software solutions to get ahead of the competition in the eCommerce market in 2021. </span></p>\n<p>Also, <a href=\"https://rampiqstg.wpengine.com/blog/b2b-seo-sales-forecasting-excel-template/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">linked here</a> is a detailed guide on SEO sales forecasting with a free Excel template to help you.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h2>7 Steps for boosting e-commerce profits</h2>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h3>1) Research your competitors</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Competitor research is the first step in creating a business growth strategy. With a clear idea of what your competitors are doing, you will be able to create more accurate, effective, and user-centric </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">marketing campaigns</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> across different channels. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With the help of a series of spying tools, you ca</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">n gather insights into different aspects of your <a href=\"https://rampiqstg.wpengine.com/who-we-help/e-commerce/\">éCommerce business</a> competitors’ strategies, and define better ways to get ahead of th</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">em. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Look into using these as part of your digital toolkit:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://sproutsocial.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sprout Social</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. This is the ultimate tool for analyzing your competitors’ social media strategies. With its help, you can analyze Facebook and Instagram metrics, visualize data, and find out the opinions of your competitors’ customers. These insights will improve your own </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">social media</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> tactics. </span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://www.mailcharts.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">MailChart.</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Finding out how your competitors handle email marketing is equally useful, given the high conversion rates within email campaigns. With MailChart, you may get helpful insights into competing email campaigns, subject lines, sending frequency, and timing. </span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://www.ispionage.com/\">iSpionage</a>. This tool is great for determining the quick-win keywords that your competitors use on their websites and blog. With its help, you can identify SEO and PPC targeted keywords, plus find other companies that are promoted in Google according to the specific topic. Grab all of this data to support competitor keyword buying for PPC, and using the right keywords in organic SEO campaigns.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>2) Improve your website user-experience</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Implementing creative and effective </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">eCommerce marketing strategies</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is a key part of driving new traffic and growth; however, they are unlikely to work if your website is not ready for a boost in traffic and has a poor user experience. The next step, especially if you are putting money into advertising, is getting your website ready for more traffic and therefore potential customers.  </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Use these and other tools to improve your website:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://website.grader.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hubspot Website Grader</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. This is a simple and intuitive tool that checks the main parameters of your website, such as page speed, performance, mobile friendliness, SEO, and security.  Using this enables you to instantly find out what points need improvement before proceeding with your marketing strategies. </span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://www.chatbot.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ChatBot</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. The incorporation of a chatbot into an eCommerce site is a widely adopted practice. This AI-powered tool can </span><a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/gilpress/2019/11/25/ai-stats-news-chatbots-increase-sales-by-67-but-87-of-consumers-prefer-humans/?sh=1102d7ee48a3\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">improve your sales by 67%</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, and what’s more, it’s quite easy to create one for your website with ChatBot.com. Its intuitive interface based on drag-and-drop functionality allows you to develop a chatbot with no coding skills. There are also numerous ready-made options on the market, and many of them integrate with social networks, such as Facebook. </span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://b2storefront.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B2Storefront.</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Switching to headless and API-driven eCommerce is one more way to improve the experience of your users while making your website more interactive. With the help of B2Storefront, you will be able to power your website with </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">headless </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">CMS. This will improve the user experience, instantly deliver marketing content across different platforms and devices, and provide a better opportunity for user experience customization. </span></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>3) Stay focused on search engine optimization (SEO)</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Every successful eCommerce business requires a smart and effective SEO strategy behind it. SEO also directly interacts with PPC campaigns; therefore deploying both is the best way to generate traffic and customers. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Since Google is constantly adjusting its algorithms to provide users with the most relevant and high-quality content, you have to pay attention to a wide number of SEO concerns. </span></p>\n<h4><b>Keyword research</b></h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Using the right keywords in your content and matching them with the user\'s intent is at the core of an effective SEO strategy. Use these tools to cover your users’ search queries and answer their questions in your content. </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://ahrefs.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ahrefs</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is one of the most popular tools for keyword research since its features are almost unlimited. With its help, you may research the whole keywords pool (depending on their competition level), find out specific and long-tailed keywords, analyze the keyword clustering of competitive websites, track your backlinks, visualize data, and get insightful reports. </span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://answerthepublic.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Answer the Public</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is a great tool for addressing your users\' concerns, and it may be quite helpful if your goal is to get on the first page of Google for a number of search queries. Answer the Public suggests the questions your users ask online, providing you with the opportunity to ultimately answer them, reaching Google Snippet, and bringing them to your eCommerce site. </span></li>\n</ul>\n<h4><b>Local search </b></h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Since </span><a href=\"https://blog.hubspot.com/marketing/local-seo-stats\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">half of the internet searches</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> are searches for local businesses, empowering your SEO strategy with location-based keywords is essential. Even if you don’t have a physical presence, local search optimization is an opportunity to get noticed by users from different locations. The following tool might be what you need: </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://localseochecklist.org/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Local SEO Checklist.</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> While you may grab location-specific keywords with the help of Ahrefs, the Local SEO Checklist will help you streamline all the other activities related to the local promotion. For example, with its help, you will be able to optimize your meta-tags, create a schema markup, set up 301 redirects, get registered, manage your profiles in high-traffic business directories, work with customers testimonials, build citations, and more. With such a powerful tool, you may expect to get a great local reach. </span></li>\n</ul>\n<h4><b>Link building</b></h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Getting a number of high-quality do-follow backlinks coming to your site is another useful Google ranking factor. Google suggests getting backlinks organically - i.e. when someone cites your content and makes a reference to your website. This process is pretty time-consuming, but you can still simplify and boost it using special link-building tools such as:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://www.semrush.com/kb/773-backlink-gap\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">SEMrush Backlink Gap Tool</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. With the help of this </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">internet marketing tool</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, you can analyze the link-building strategies of your competitors. It helps you identify the backlinks your competitors have, which means you can implement a more effective guest blog outreach approach. </span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://adsy.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Adsy</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> lets you automate your guest posting and link-building strategies. With its help, you can reach out to relevant blogs and websites accepting guest posts, create guest content, and get valuable backlinks, in addition to reaching potential new customers. </span></li>\n</ul>\n<h4><b>Content writing</b></h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It’s worth mentioning that content is at the heart of any </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">eCommerce website</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and marketing strategy. Thankfully there are numerous tools to make your SEO-optimized and guest content even better for </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">search engines</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, to help customers find you:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://www.grammarly.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Grammarly.</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> With the Grammarly Premium version, you can fix writing mistakes, typos, and extra spaces, plus make better word choices and follow a clearer sentence structure. Using Grammarly, you can also check your content for plagiarism.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://hemingwayapp.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hemingway app.</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Making blogs and articles readable, alongside copy on web pages and product pages, is important for Google because the longer web visitors are on pages the better a website performs in rankings. Hemingway, named after the famous author, Ernst Hemingway, known for writing shorter more engaging sentences in an era when many authors still wrote in larger paragraphs, helps writers in the Internet era produce shorter more effective passages of text, for blogs, articles and on web pages. </span></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>4) Gain valuable insights into your web visitors</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In this era of data-driven and personalized marketing, you need a clear idea of what web visitors are doing, why, and to gain as many insights as possible so you can tailor the experience more effectively to drive sales.  </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The following </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">eCommerce analytics tools</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> allow for gaining these insights quickly:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://www.hotjar.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hotjar.</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> This is a customer behavior analysis tool based on AI technology. Using it, you will be able to find out your customers\' behavior patterns, create visual heatmaps, and record </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">website visitors’ </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">sessions in real-time. Hotjay also lets you create user surveys and get firsthand opinions about their impressions of your business. This is one of the best solutions for obtaining real-time and real-life analytical insights, and you can use them for your eCommerce website development and user journey improvement. </span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://www.reviewtrackers.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ReviewTrackers</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. This social listening software allows for staying updated on what your customers share about your brand online. When each new review is created and posted on Google My Business or other review platforms, you get an alert. With the help of ReviewTrackers, you will be able to carefully manage your online reputation and </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">brand awareness,</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> monitor </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">existing customers</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">’ satisfaction, and instantly respond to users’ feedback, strengthening your relationships and solving their complaints. </span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>5) Start attracting new customers</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After your website has improved conversion rates and SEO positions, and you are well-informed on your customers’ specifics, behaviors, and opinions, it\'s time to attract new potential customers. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here are a couple of actionable lead generation tactics you can implement:</span></p>\n<h4><b>Lead magnets</b></h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lead magnets are the most powerful tools for </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">lead generation</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and capture. They work well for pulling potential customers into your sales funnel and collecting a </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">potential customers\'</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> database.  Lead magnets take the form of non-intrusive pop-ups offering something valuable (for example, a discount or valuable piece of content) in exchange for new users’ contact details. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Think about the offer that you will share with the help of a lead magnet. It should be attractive and valuable. For example, many </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">eCommerce websites</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> offer a discount for the first purchase or free shipping. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">eCommerce tool</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> will help you create them. </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://optinmonster.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">OptinMonster.</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> With the help of OptinMonster, you may create attractive and effective lead magnets, embed them on your website, and set them up according to your users’ behavior. For example, a lead magnet may appear when the user shows the intent of leaving the website, or when dwelling on the product page for several minutes without proceeding to the </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">checkout process</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span></li>\n</ul>\n<h4><b>Search engine marketing (SEM)</b></h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">SEM is the winning strategy when you need to attract new shares of potential customers. Use </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Google marketing tools</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> for this purpose: </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://ads.google.com/home/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Google Ads</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> This is the core tool for setting up PPC or PPA advertising. With its help, you will be able to pick the target keywords that cause your ad to appear, add a headline and ad copy text, and most importantly, carefully segment your </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">target audience</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> according to multiple parameters such as age, location, behavior, or interests. eCommerce websites can also pay to put product listings directly in search results, so when someone searches for “blue sweater”, your product listing with an image and price shows up. </span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://analytics.google.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Google Analytics.</span></a> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To analyze the results of your SEM campaigns, connect Google Analytics to your website. It will give you the opportunity to get custom and visualized reports, revealing the weak and strong points of your campaigns. </span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>6) Implement email marketing</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After you’ve attracted a new influx of potential customers, with the help of SEM marketing, PPC, social media, and lead magnets, you need to keep them engaged using email marketing. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We suggest using a comprehensive </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">email marketing tool for businesses</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to manage, track, and analyze their campaigns from a single place: </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><a href=\"https://www.activecampaign.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Active Campaign</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is one of the most popular email marketing solutions that are equally suitable for </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">small businesses</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and eCommerce companies. With it, you can create awesome newsletter templates, set up sending sequences, test the users’ responses, and conduct A/B testing. It can even trigger site messages, manage live chat communication, and analyze your sales. </span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>7) Encourage sales from those who’ve left without buying</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Since the modern sales funnel is cyclical, you need to close its last stage, meaning it’s time to automatize repeat purchases. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">OptinMonster, which we have already used to create lead magnets, can be a good solution in this case. This software enables you to work with abandoned carts, set up retargeting campaigns, personalize content marketing, and much more.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"row_img\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"719\" img_size=\"1000x500\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"720\" img_size=\"1000x500\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\n<h2><strong>Conclusion</strong></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The list of </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">eCommerce marketing tools </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">used to streamline your online promotion could go on and on. We provided you with an ultimate toolkit, which when used smartly may significantly improve your ROI and reduce costs. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, managing all the processes on your own may be overwhelming, especially if you need to focus on more crucial business tasks, like building your audience’s trust or entering a new market. In this case, the wise decision can be to outsource your marketing strategy development and implementation to tech and market-savvy vendors. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://rampiqstg.wpengine.com/\">Rampiq digital marketing agency</a> will be glad to hear about the marketing challenges your </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://rampiqstg.wpengine.com/who-we-help/e-commerce/\">eCommerce </a>business </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">faces and would be happy to implement a powerful strategy designed to boost your sales! </span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\n','7 Steps to Enhance Your e-Commerce Business and Boost Sales','Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pa