 We focus on every detail of the journey to recommend key optimizations that will enhance the customer experience and boost sales.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"398\" img_size=\"full\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Dedicated marketing support</h4>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While you focus on mission-critical operations, a dedicated account manager will keep you informed on campaign progress with detailed reports and marketing plans. We will never charge for extra hours without prior approval from you.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"411\" img_size=\"full\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Industry best practices</h4>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">e-commerce marketing agency</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> employs white hat practices and adheres to industry standards, especially when it comes to compliance with Google guidelines. This is </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ecommerce online marketing</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> implemented the right way.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"563\" img_size=\"full\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Constant innovation</h4>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Creative marketing strategies give your brand a leg up. Rampiq keeps your campaigns relevant by incorporating the most up-to-date guidance from digital e-commerce marketing platforms, including Google, Facebook, LinkedIn, and Instagram. </span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"our_advantages_btn_row\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h6>Let\'s start planning out my campaign!</h6>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-298\" role=\"img\" src=\"https://rampiqstg.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Arrow-2.svg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /> <a href=\"/contact-us/\">Get Started</a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_col