rl(https://rampiqstg.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/image_1024x1024@2x.png?id=759) !important;}\" el_class=\"client_overview_right\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Client\'s business goals</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As a startup, Basepaws needs to continuously grow its revenue and provide regular reports to the stakeholders in order to secure further investment. That is why the client turned to Rampiq with its biggest goal – to increase the number of purchases and sign-ups for cat DNA tests through paid ad campaigns and provide insightful analytics. During the initial business analysis stage, Rampiq team also discovered that data gathered on existing paid channels is not structured and informative enough to see if these channels bring results and value to the client. </span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section el_class=\"client_challenges_section\" css=\".vc_custom_1621512515429{background-color: #f1f3f5 !important;}\"][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>Client\'s challenges</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lack of visibility across paid channels</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Low brand awareness in the feline health niche</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Need fro higher revenue to get additional investment for startups</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>Solutions applied</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/6\"][vc_single_image image=\"262\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"5/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4><b>PPC campaigns takeover and restructuring</b></h4>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With target audience and industry specifics in mind, Rampiq team set up three different types of PPC ad campaigns aimed at different goals. Brand awareness campaigns focused on increasing brand presence in the niche and improving product recognition among consumers. Conversion campaigns were aimed at increasing the number of product purchases, thus bringing transactions and increasing ROAS. While Basepaws had a very strong client-oriented email marketing strategy, the number of signups on its website was not increasing. For the purpose of driving more leads into the sales funnel and providing them with access to relevant information to help them make a buying decision, Rampiq also set up sign-up campaigns. </span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/6\"][vc_single_image image=\"263\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"5/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n<b>Multi-channel analytics setup</b>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rampiq team set up OWOX BI analytics platform to facilitate and streamline multi-channel reporting. As a result, the client has actionable reports that provide a good understanding of the value of each advertising platform and campaign, and help establish clear KPIs for each campaign individually. Rampiq also provides interactive reports in Google Data Studio and automated Google Sheets reports to help the client make smarter data-driven decisions for the benefit of the business. </span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/6\"][vc_single_image image=\"264\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"5/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4><b>Audience testing</b></h4>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To efficiently expand the reach of marketing campaigns, Rampiq team сonducted a series of experiments to test new audiences in Facebook, Google Ads, Quora, and Pinterest. Based on the data received, Basepaws got a more detailed profile for their ideal prospects and customers. This also allowed Rampiq to adjust existing marketing strategies to reach better sales results. </span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section el_class=\"client_results_section\"][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Results</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thanks to thoughtful ad campaign setup and detailed ongoing monitoring and analysis, Rampiq helped increase transparency and visibility across all paid channels. With clear KPIs and campaign performance results on hand, Rampiq team helped make result-oriented decisions aimed to decrease client’s spendings, increase revenue, and build stronger brand awareness in the feline health niche.</span></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<ul class=\"tabs_caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n 	<li>Before seo</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"active\">After seo</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"client_tabs_content\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"client_tabs_content_left\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Low</h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">number of product purchases</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>Low</strong></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">website conversion rate</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>Lack</strong></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">of visibility across paid ad campaign efficacy</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>Low</strong></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">number of website visitors</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"client_tabs_content_right\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Client\'s feedback:</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_t