c_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Client\'s business goals</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After initially turning to Rampiq through a referral, OMI has become one of our key trusted business partners. OMI’s goal was straightforward – to acquire more leads through the website and then help them convert into prospects. Initial business analysis helped the Rampiq team to identify the existing website’s weak spots and come up with a strategy for its revamp. The client was also looking for an experienced content development team to create content for new landing pages and the blog and optimize them to rank high in search engines. </span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section el_class=\"client_challenges_section\" css=\".vc_custom_1621512515429{background-color: #f1f3f5 !important;}\"][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>Client\'s challenges</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Under-performing website</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lack of content to drive leads through the funnel</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Not enough qualified leads</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2>Solutions applied</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/6\"][vc_single_image image=\"262\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"5/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4><b>Niche analysis and SEO strategy development</b></h4>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Before the redesign, 95% of the site\'s users were landing on the blog while the services pages weren\'t generating traffic and weren\'t bringing conversions. Rampiq analyzed the competitors’ websites to come up with an SEO strategy aimed at improving website search rankings and traffic increase. Once the new website went live, Rampiq team expanded OMI\'s digital presence with a solid SEO and outreach strategy to make sure key customers can find the client’s business online. We applied best practices in guest posting and created company profiles in industry-leading business directories and top lists. With carefully thought-out on-page and off-page SEO activities, Rampiq helps OMI reach its most valuable audience and provide them with relevant information about the company’s key services and competitive advantages. </span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/6\"][vc_single_image image=\"263\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"5/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4><b>Tech SEO report development &amp; complete support of custom website redesign</b></h4>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rampiq analyzed OMI’s website performance for technical SEO errors that prevented it from reaching its ranking goals, and provided thorough guidelines for the website’s redesign. As a part of the technical audit, our team also measured the website\'s loading speed and provided recommendations for improving user experience. To make landing pages more informative and visually appealing for users and to ease navigation, we redeveloped the site’s structure, introduced new layouts, and created high-converting copy for the new service pages. Additionally, the Rampiq development team set up OMI’s blog. </span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/6\"][vc_single_image image=\"264\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"5/6\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4><b>Dedicated content marketing team</b></h4>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our content marketing specialists studied the niche extensively to get into it and now work with OMI’s digital transformation experts to regularly update the site’s blog with expert content about CRM and SaaS. We constantly research new content formats and topics to deliver key information on the company’s expertise in a way that is not only compelling but also ranks high in search engines. Moreover, Rampiq has become a dedicated content development partner not just for OMI but also its key clients. </span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section el_class=\"client_results_section\"][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Results</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Over the years, Rampiq and OMI have built a strong mutually beneficial partnership based on trust and respect. After helping OMI roll out a new website, Rampiq took up the role of a dedicated content marketing team, thus eliminating the need to hire in-house specialists. The content marketing strategy created by Rampiq helped to increase brand awareness in the CRM managed service industry and bring in more qualified leads.</span></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<ul class=\"tabs_caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\r\n 	<li>Before seo</li>\r\n 	<li class=\"active\">After seo</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"client_tabs_content\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"client_tabs_content_left\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Low</h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">volume of qualified leads</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Low</h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">number of websites’ visitors</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>18</strong></h3>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">niche-related keywords in top 10 results</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"client_tabs_c