igital marketing service</a> you need for your online success, including pay-per-click, search engine optimization, digital strategy, and more.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Known for its massive collection of data-driven content, Clutch is a B2B review and market resource platform that covers the design, development, business services, and marketing industries. With millions upon millions of users, Clutch is known as one of the fastest-growing startups in the United States. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br />\r\nClutch has an esteemed certification program that brings light to socially and economically disadvantaged firms. The certification program allows companies to self-identify their LGBTQ, veteran, and racial minority identities.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"734\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With that being said, we are absolutely proud to be a certified top-notch </span><a href=\"https://clutch.co/agencies/digital-marketing/women-owned\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">women owned business</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> on Clutch! Rampiq Agency is thankful for this opportunity to empower our team.</span></p>\r\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“Throughout various industries, women-owned companies provide a unique and important perspective that’s often overlooked,”</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> stated Clutch Revenue Operations Analyst Carolyn Rider. </span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“We want to highlight these companies for everything that they bring to the table, from their thoughtfulness to their detail-oriented mindsets.”</span></i></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are genuinely stoked to see what opportunities this will bring to our team. We dedicate this certification to our clients who understand, trust, and support us. Without them, our team wouldn’t be here today. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hear what our clients say about us:</span></p>\r\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“It was a pleasure working with them because they were very professional, and they were mindful of our needs, tone of voice, and the way we communicate with others. They never interfered in the text itself, and just created all the marketing stuff. They were very responsive.”</span></i></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">— Managing Editor, Simple</span></p>\r\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“Their hard-working attitude towards any task and willingness to drive value says it all. We worked with a lot of marketing agencies before, but Rampiq is truly the agency that your business needs to grow sustainably.” </span></i></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">— Co-Founder &amp; CTO, SmartApp</span></p>\r\n<p><b>The Hottest on The Manifest</b></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Aside from our milestone from Clutch, we are also thrilled to share with you our latest recognition from The Manifest, a business news site that acts as a credible source of B2B wisdom for users.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rampiq Agency has been </span><a href=\"https://themanifest.com/ppc/women-owned/agencies#rampiqagency\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">listed on The Manifest</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">’s ranking of the global top 10 women owned pay-per-click agencies for 2021! This is wonderful news to us.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Looking for a <a href=\"https://rampiqstg.wpengine.com/who-we-help/in-house/\">digital marketing partner</a>? Let’s talk. </span><a href=\"https://rampiqstg.wpengine.com/contact-us/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Send us a message</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> and tell us all about your business, needs, and goals. We are looking forward to hearing from you.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\r\n','Rampiq Agency Is a Proud Certified Top-Tier Women Owned Agency on Clutch','','publish','open','open','','rampiq-certified-top-women-owned-agency-clutch','','','2022-09-02 12:38:18','2022-09-02 12:38:18','',0,'https://rampiqstg.wpengine.com/?p=732',0,'post','',0),(733,1,'2021-06-25 19:21:10','2021-06-25 19:21:10','','Clutch badge','','inherit','open','closed','','clutch-badge','','','2021-06-25 19:24:48','2021-06-25 19:24:48','',732,'https://rampiqstg.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Clutch-badge.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(734,1,'2021-06-29 13:27:47','2021-06-29 13:27:47','','Women_Option_1','','inherit','open','closed','','women_option_1','','','2021-06-29 13:27:47','2021-06-29 13:27:47','',732,'https://rampiqstg.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Women_Option_1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(736,1,'2021-06-30 08:01:54','2021-06-30 08:01:54','','Arrow_svg','','inherit','open','closed','','arrow_svg','','','2021-06-30 08:01:54','2021-06-30 08:01:54','',0,'https://rampiqstg.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Arrow_svg.svg',0,'attachment','image/svg+xml',0),(737,1,'2021-06-30 11:08:41','2021-06-30 11:08:41','','bg (1)','','inherit','open','closed','','bg-1','','','2021-06-30 11:08:41','2021-06-30 11:08:41','',0,'https://rampiqstg.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/bg-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(739,1,'2021-06-30 21:46:07','2021-06-30 21:46:07','','Brad Banyas-2','','inherit','open','closed','','brad-banyas-2','','','2021-06-30 21:46:07','2021-06-30 21:46:07','',652,'https://rampiqstg.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Brad-Banyas-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(740,1,'2021-06-30 21:53:11','2021-06-30 21:53:11','','Снимок экрана 2021-07-01 в 00.48.57','','inherit','open','closed','','%d1%81%d0%bd%d0%b8%d0%bc%d0%be%d0%ba-%d1%8d%d0%ba%d1%80%d0%b0%d0%bd%d0%b0-2021-07-01-%d0%b2-00-48-57',